729465f-a.title: Richmond: Richmond Terrace - Winant Street
729465f-a.text:
Richmond Terrace, east from Winant Street, showing the Bayonne Bridge at Newark Avenue, and the Dean Linseed Oil
Works (background) at John Street.

November 4, 1931
P.L. Sperr
